title: Nickelodeon All-Stars Tennis v1.0.3
description:
Serve It, Smash It, Win It, Slime It!

Test your tennis skills against some of your favourite Nickelodeon characters as you climb the All Stars Tennis ranks from Rookie to World Champion! 

Play through 9 tournaments from the Bikini Bottom Cup and TMNT Challenge to the Down Under Slam. Unlock awesome playable characters, outfits and power rackets including SpongeBob SquarePants, the Teenage Mutant NinjaTurtles, and Sanjay and Craig!

Fast and fun gameplay and an awesome range of play styles, unlockable equipment, player customisation and tournaments. You can even challenge friends for Tennis glory!
